Many visitors claim that receiving official status in our country is not so easy.
The reason is the bureaucratic obstacles and the difficulties of the language itself.
Besides, legalization costs money: from twelve thousand to sixteen thousand rubles.
However, a false inscription can be made quickly and for only fifteen hundred rubles.
