He has severe asthma, difficulty breathing, constant coughing and irritation of the eyes from toxic fumes.
At 27 years old, Anto has been playing hide and seek for three years in Kawah Ijen, whose sulfur has already started to pay off despite covering his face with a mask and special glasses.
He has asthma, difficulty breathing, constant coughing, and irritation of the eyes from the toxic gases released by the volcano.
